        <num>CC 887</num>
        <heading>887.  Representation of decedent whose succession was renounced</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 887.  Representation of decedent whose succession was renounced
One who has renounced his right to succeed to another may still enjoy
the right of representation with respect to that other.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=111038</p>
